    <h2> Surveying done the right way</h2>
    <div class="cont">
        Formtech Land Surveying, Inc is a Florida Corporation offering comprehensive
        land surveying and mapping services to both private sector and public agency clients.
        Our firm specializes in providing land surveying and mapping with the latest techniques
        in order to quickly and accurately provide our clients with the services they need to
        keep their projects on track. As professionals, we guarantee our work for many years to come,
        and our attention is personalized in the office and as well as with our field crew members.
        With more than twenty years of combined experience, our team provides surveying services
        divided into three categories of projects: Real Estate, Construction and Government.
